sentences: Laurence Mark 'Laurie' Wisefield (born 27 August 1953) is an English guitarist, known for his contributions to Wishbone Ash during the 1970s and 1980s.
The group released three albums through Columbia Records between 1971 and 1974.
In 2002, Wisefield joined the musical cast of We Will Rock You.

sentences: As well as performing live with the musical, Wisefield appeared on the 2002 cast recording, and accompanied the performance at the 2002 Party at the Palace to celebrate the Golden Jubilee of Elizabeth II.
